name: Google Daydream - XR Framework (Converted Sketch File)
description:
Googles Daydream project from 2016 - 2017 is one of the best XR files available. Its concept of DMMs, proper viewing angles, and positioning is super important.


I couldn't find this bad boy on Figma so I converted it from a sketch file they released years ago.


Love you google daydream team!
